        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 18 Quiz – Game State and UI Foundation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of game state management, UI rendering, and DOM updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- Game state objects
- Rendering functions
- DOM updates and display
- Template literals for HTML
- updateUI patterns&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 18 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
